# Autofocus

Take pictures using autofocus.

1. Slide the focus mode selector to S or C (page 66).

   !Focus Mode Selector

2. Choose an AF mode (page 68).

3. Choose the position and size of the focus frame (page 70).

   !Focus Frame Adjustment

4. Take pictures.
